  "description": "Use this skill when writing Apex triggers or classes that interact with CaseMilestone records \u2014 completing milestones, detecting violations, or reacting to SLA state changes. Trigger keywords: CaseMilestone trigger, auto-complete milestone Apex, milestone violation polling, CompletionDate write pattern. NOT for entitlement process admin setup, milestone configuration in Setup UI, or Flow-based milestone actions.",
